The paper deals with distributed optimization algorithms for large-scale regularized loss minimization, which is a common problem in machine learning and data analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.NA (Numerical Analysis), and cs.MA (Multi-Agent Systems).
